node.text:
Repost from @joshuadenne 
Who do you spend time with?
-
One of the days changed my life is when I heard Jim Rohn ask me these questions:
Who are you around?
What do they have you saying?
What do they have you thinking?
What do they have you doing?
Most importantly, what do they have you becoming?
And lastly, Is that ok?

Perhaps “they” didn’t “have” me doing anything... Yet I had never given it much thought. 
At the time I heard this, most of the people around me were not moving in a positive direction. Although they were decent people, they had the tendency to perceive the world as negative and spent their free time partying and dreading Monday’s...
They were not the healthiest relationships. -
I decided that day to surround myself with people who had the answers I was looking for, the people who had the results I was looking for and most importantly the people who I most desired to become like. -
At first most of the people who I wanted to be like didn’t know I existed, and if they did then I imagine that they were not wanting to be around me 😂
-
I found these people in books, audios and at business seminars and Church. I consistently showed up and worked on myself extremely hard and eventually found myself surround by the people who changed my life for the better!
-
It's up to you to seek out people who will elevate your mindset and push you towards the success you desire for your life! Find a a coach or mentor in the areas of life you want improvement in, hire them if you can. Read their books, listen to their podcasts and follow their social pages and you’ll begin the process that can transform your life for the better!!

node.title: Who Do You Spend Time With?

node.text:
Repost from @joshuadenne 
What do you read?
-
It's fascinating to think that, today, in 2020 we have access to more information than any other generation of humans in recorded history.. Yet, it seems that most people prefer to only watch mindless entertainment on Youtube, Netflix or other platforms rather than reading quality material.
(Entertainment is great but, like everything else in moderation and in my opinion after you have filled your mind with useful and quality content)
Books and other reading material gives you access some of the most brilliant minds on the planet and spark your imagination!
🧠
When I realized that I could learn in a few days what it took others a life time to learn simply by reading a book it got me so excited that I began a journey that has revolutionized my life and enriched me in more ways than I can count.
😃
Reading can shave years, if not decades, off your learning curve and put you light years ahead of those who do not.
📖
Do you have a favorite book?
Please share it in the comments below and if you dare please share why it’s your favorite. 📚

node.text:
Repost from @joshuadenne
-
What do you find yourself listening to most often?👂 -
What we listen to on a daily basis influences our thoughts in a major way. 
I believe it is vital to stand guard at the doors of our mind and only allow in that which helps you achieve the life you are aiming towards. 
Our ears are those doors and sadly most people allow anything to enter inside... perhaps it’s because their guard is a sleep 😴 🧐
Do you remember as a middle schooler picking up the language and different expressions of speech from your peers?
Have you ever memeorized a song that absolutely annoys the $&@$ out of you? 🤣
You hate the song, but there it is playing in your head like a broken record. 😩
💻 
There is an saying among computer programmers: “Garbage In, Garbage Out.”
Meaning we get out what we put in.. Therefore, may I suggest we avoid allowing  garbage to get in and instead, purposefully inject quality positive information in? 😎
Personally, I enjoy podcasts and audiobooks.
Do you have a favorite podcast and or audiobook? If so please tag or post in the comments so we can all enjoy!

From our newest IGTV Series with @joshuadenne —
What do you look at on a daily basis? 👀
—
Behavioral Science tells us that whatever we see consistently will eventually Influence our thoughts, which in turn, lead us into action. Our actions determine our results. Our results provide us with our lifestyle. Therefore, should we desire to change our lifestyle, it stands to reason that we must change what we consume through our eyes.😃

node.text:
Today on the Build Your Empire podcast @caseyadams1 sat down with the founder of Onyx, Travis Bott.

During this conversation they went over what ONYX is, and how it's completely changing the game when it comes to utilizing crypto currency.

Travis Bott is apart of over 27+ companies, and he's been a true entrepreneur all of his life. Onyx is a lifestyle brand that gives it's members the opportunity to enhance the quality of their life.

They have multiple memberships tiers, and have access to some of the most luxurious travel destinations in the world. Also, Onyx gives you the ability to utilize your crypto currency anywhere in the world by using one of their membership cards.

We're excited to introduce you to such an amazing company, and we look forward to getting you involved.

If you'd like to get involved with ONYX then send us a DM saying "ONYX" and we'll be sending you over more information.

node.title: Build Your Empire - Onyx Lifestyle with @trav.cass

node.text:
Welcome To Empire Day!

Empire Day Is BYE's New Podcast Segment Where Someone From The Team Drops BOMBS On The Fundamentals Of Being An Entrepreneur!

Today CEO Casey Adams Sits Down With Business Partner and Philanthropist Joshua Denne. Together The Two Go In Depth On The Essential Aspect Of Having A Mentor.

Having A Mentor Can Help An Entrepreneur At Any Levels Grow And Exceed In Life And Business Alike. 
Listen In To Learn More In This 15min Empire Day!

Follow BuildYourEmpire :
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/buildyourempire/

Follow Joshua Denne :
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/joshuadenne/

Follow Casey Adams : 
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/caseyadams1/

See what goes on at the Build Your Empire House:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMBxxBy-ADkrjuC2So70H0w

Keep building your empire! Make sure to DOWNLOAD and SUBSCRIBE to the Build Your Empire Podcast!

Stay tuned for the Next Empire Builder. #buildyourempire

node.text: Grant Cardone is a true example of an Empire Builder. Follow @grantcardone for more information!📍

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Build Your Empire® in Paradise Valley, Arizona with @joshuadenne, @codygrandadam, @john.malott, and @najmalott. May be an image of text that says 'Today's humans do not need terrorists to disrupt peace in the world- they are doing it themselves quite well BUILDYOUREMPIRE'.

node.text: Do you agree with this?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Build Your Empire® in The Emerald City Seattle Washington with @joshuadenne, @codygrandadam, @hardcorecloser, @john.malott, and @najmalott. May be an image of text that says 'Quarantine is when you restrict the movement of sick people. Tyranny is when you restrict the movement of healthy people BUILDYOUREMPIRE'.

node.text: What are your thoughts?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Build Your Empire® in Paradise Valley, Arizona with @joshuadenne, @john.malott, and @najmalott. May be an image of text that says 'What problem does your business solve? BUILDYOUREMPIRE JUI 28 2019'.

node.text: The best businesses provide real solutions to peoples and / or society’s challenges. Tell us what you solve. Bless someone.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Build Your Empire® on June 28, 2021 tagging @john.malott, and @najmalott. May be an image of text that says '5 things to give up: 1.Overthinking 2. Fearing change 3. Living in the past 4. Negative self-talk 5. Trying to please everyone BUILDYOUREMPIRE'.

node.text: Some times you need to give up to go up.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Build Your Empire® on May 04, 2021 tagging @joshuadenne, @john.malott, @najmalott, and @osnapactivelifestyle. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'IF YOU COULD WRITE A NOTE TO YOUR YOUNGER SELF, WHAT WOULD YOU SAY IN ONLY TWO WORDS? BUILDYOUREMPIRE'.

node.text: Let’s reflect..

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Build Your Empire® in Paradise Valley, Arizona with @joshuadenne, @john.malott, @najmalott, and @osnapactivelifestyle. May be an image of text that says 'Say something nice about yourself. I am BUILDYOUREMPIRE'.

node.text: It’s easy to be negative. Let’s switch it up today.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Build Your Empire® in Paradise Valley, Arizona with @joshuadenne, @thematthewmorgan, @john.malott, @najmalott, and @osnapactivelifestyle. May be an image of text that says 'did you know? Eating 4 almonds a day helps you lower cholesterol, improves hair quality, prevents heart diseases, helps fight wrinkles, helps with weight loss and improves brain activities. BUILDYOUREMPIRE'.

node.text: This may be a bit controversial in a time when health care is driven by political agendas and big Pharmaceutical companies 🤷🏼‍♂️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Build Your Empire® in Paradise Valley, Arizona with @joshuadenne, @john.malott, @najmalott, and @osnapactivelifestyle. May be an image of text that says 'Procrastination is the arrogant assumption that God owes you another opportunity to do what you had time to do BUILDYOUREMPIRE'.

node.text: Let that sink in while you think about doing something, but don’t 🤷🏼‍♂️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Build Your Empire® in Paradise Valley, Arizona with @cleverinvestor, @joshuadenne, @codygrandadam, @john.malott, and @osnapactivelifestyle. May be an image of text that says 'Big money in sick people BUILDYOUREMPIRE'.

node.text: True or false?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Build Your Empire® in Miami, Florida with @cleverinvestor, @joshuadenne, @codygrandadam, @john.malott, @najmalott, and @osnapactivelifestyle. May be an image of text that says 'WHATEVER YOU CAN'T DEFEND PROMOTE BUILDYOUREMPIRE'.

node.text: Stop trying to hide your faults and flaws. They will find out anyway. Take the ammunition away from the haters. Put it all in the light on your terms 💯

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Build Your Empire® in Paradise Valley, Arizona. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'THERE IS ABOUT TO BE A SHIFT IN YOUR LIFE. GET READY FOR YOUR BLESSINGS. MIRACLES ARE ON THE WAY. TYPE "YES" IF YOU AGREE BUILDYOUREMPIRE'.

node.text: First you receive in your mind, then you manifest it in the physical. YES!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Build Your Empire® in Paradise Valley, Arizona with @cleverinvestor, @tessaabellaa, @joshuadenne, @codygrandadam, @john.malott, @najmalott, and @osnapactivelifestyle. May be an image of text that says 'SERVICE TO MANY LEADS TO GREATNESS BUILDYOUREMPIRE'.

node.text: Despite what the perception may be. Greatness is attained through one way and one way only: SERVICE TO OTHERS!
